Class RQI_I01_GUARANTOR_INSURANCE

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v251.group.RQI_I01_GUARANTOR_INSURANCE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class RQI_I01_GUARANTOR_INSURANCE
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a RQI_I01_GUARANTOR_INSURANCE group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: GT1 (Guarantor) optional repeating
    • 2: RQI_I01_INSURANCE (a Group object) repeating
